parameters.description:
What tag or branch should be built?
Branches have a 'v' in front, while tags do not.
Branches are updated/patched, while tags are not.
The site is better off using branches, so the API docs don't have buggy info.
parameters.name: tags_to_build

parameters.description:
What tags should the site display in the dropdown?
The order should match the tags_to_build parameter exactly.
Example: "master;1.2.1" matches tags_to_build if it had "master;1.2.0".
The job would build the 1.2.0 branch, but display 1.2.1 on the site.
parameters.name: tag_list

parameters.description:
The fork to use. Can be a contributor's development fork. Production should be:
https://github.com/apache/incubator-mxnet.git
parameters.name: fork

parameters.description:
Use your staging server addess, like:
http://107.21.90.138/

Or production address, like:
http://mxnet.incubator.apache.org/

Trailing slash is required.
parameters.name: domain
